{"data":[{"date":"15:24 09/08","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-courtois-toi-real-madrid.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng k\u1ebb thua sau khi Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng k\u1ebb thua sau khi Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Nguoi-thang-ke-thua-sau-khi-Thibaut-Courtois-toi-Real-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, song The Blues v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Christophe Henrotay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Courtois \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u xin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London bu\u00f4ng tha cho th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Courtois mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real, song Chelsea l\u1ea1i ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. H\u1ecd \u0111ang ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho Chelsea, h\u1ecd n\u00ean t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. Khi m\u00e0 Hazard, Kante hay Giroud tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Chelsea th\u00ec Courtois v\u1eabn \u1edf l\u1ea1i B\u1ec9, anh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Chelsea.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992 cho Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCourtois k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real Madrid, anh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m nguy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nu\u00f4i tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kante, Giroud, Morata hay Hazard, song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Courtois \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/Vi-sao-Real-Madrid-mua-Thibaut-Courtois-van-chua-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Thibaut Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb ph\u00eda ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Courtois ra \u0111i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Kepa, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keylor Navas ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois van dang rat muon den Real\" title=\"Courtois v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chelsea-chieu-mo-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-thanh-cong-tu-Athletic-Bilbao-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThibaut Courtois l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Real cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Marina Granovskaia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marina Granovskaia l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n b\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, song d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Granovskaia ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marina Granovskaia dang khong lam tot cong viec cua minh\" title=\"Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Chelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Jorginho l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Alisson, Golovin hay Gonzalo Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Rugani, Pjanic hay Ramsey c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia c\u00f2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Courtois, b\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i phi\u00ean Ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a H\u00e8 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ri\u00eang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Granovskaia.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Kepa Arrizabalaga</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Kepa Arrizabalaga ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Athletic Bilbao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa la ai\" title=\"Kepa l\u00e0 ai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/kepa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1edbi 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi Bilbao, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London chi ra, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Blues anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng cao h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Bilbao r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, Kepa kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng n\u1eefa, c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Keylor Navas</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m qua, Keylor Navas \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Real l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Keylor Navas\" title=\"thu mon Keylor Navas\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0908-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Keylor Navas c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Keylor Navas \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 2 trong khung g\u1ed7, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKeylor Navas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Thibaut Courtois: &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Courtois l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Navas tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2176","checkdouble":"194113"},{"date":"15:42 09/08","title":"B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Uzbekistan, Palestine v\u00e0 Oman \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong m\u1eaft gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Bola cho r\u1eb1ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o d\u1ea5u m\u1ed1c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/photo-1-15337765426941939351668.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u1edd b\u00e1o Indonesia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft 12 trong s\u1ed1 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 ASIAD t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 \"2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafc b\u00e9n l\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi g\u1ecdi danh s\u00e1ch 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Bola c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan.\u00a0V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194093.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194093.html\">C\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan, \u00f4ng Steve Darby \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2175","checkdouble":"194114"},{"date":"16:44 09/08","title":"V\u1eeba sang Chelsea, bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 l\u00e0m huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/bom-tan-71-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea-muon-gianh-chuc-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n mua Rakitic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p duy nh\u1ea5t Verratti l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/2-doi-bong-o-ligue-1-dai-chien-vi-rakitic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Rakitic, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i PSG v\u00e0 Monaco th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-bang-sao-khung-cua-barca-172-182166.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Rakitic</span>, Mourinho nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco c\u00f3 Rakitic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Ivan Rakitic b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i sau khi \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Iniesta.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" title=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/liverpool-tranh-ivan-rakitic-voi-mu-trong-mua-he-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ivan Rakitic r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1edfi Monaco kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi PSG n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Rakitic r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd vi ph\u1ea1m Lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf Ligue 1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Rakitic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Barca. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Monaco v\u00e0 PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Rakitic l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2174","checkdouble":"194116"},{"date":"16:29 09/08","title":"Mateo Kovacic CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mateo-kovacic-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-chelsea.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, ph\u00eda Real Madrid th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mateo-kovacic-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-chelsea.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mateo Kovacic ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t hay d\u1edf th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1eabn quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea</span> ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Chelsea, anh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Sarri c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kovacic n\u00f3i g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Chelsea?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ng\u00e0y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic\" title=\"Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kovacic-bai-toan-kho-danh-cho-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kovacic r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u00f4i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng HLV v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u00f4i nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Kovacic, ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng c\u1eadu \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Kovacic s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2173","checkdouble":"194117"},{"date":"16:17 09/08","title":"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic: HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kovacic-bai-toan-kho-danh-cho-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic t\u1eeb Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng gi\u00fap anh ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kovacic khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Dinamo Zagreb. Nh\u01b0ng Inter \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i b\u1edfi Kovacic t\u1eebng t\u1eadp th\u1eed \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 10 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f3t v\u00e0o tai Kovacic. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Javier Zanetti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh l\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Ro \u201cb\u00e9o\u201d l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 n\u0103m 1997.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Kovacic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao ngay cho chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Anh kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Walter Mazzarri m\u00f9a 2013/14 v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 bao khi Roberto Mancini c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn. C\u00e1c HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng Kovacic ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng trao m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Chelsea-chieu-mo-Kovacic-HLV-Sarri-doi-dien-bai-toan-kho-giai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Pirlo khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Inter</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u00f9ng, Kovacic b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Real Madrid n\u0103m 2015 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi Zanetti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u00e0o anh. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Samir Handanovic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kovacic \u201cc\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c HLV ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Kovacic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Italia, Kovacic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t Andrea Pirlo m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Giovanni Trapattoni mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 Kovacic l\u00e0 \u201cs\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa Kaka v\u00e0 Seedorf\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 th\u1eadt, Kovacic c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Anh r\u00ea b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec7u ngh\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u00edch ch\u01a1i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1ecf neo v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAndrea Stramaccioni, HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Kovacic t\u1ea1i Inter kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cKovacic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 10 nh\u01b0 khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf\u201d. C\u00f2n Rafa Benitez c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u00f4ng lung: \u201cKovacic kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t\u201d. V\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Kovacic t\u1ea1i Real cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic\" title=\"Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/161159-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKovacic x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 r\u00ea b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 90 ph\u00fat m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Anh c\u0169ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 9 v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n m\u1ed7i 90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 14 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pha t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong top 25 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mateo Kovacic</span> b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. 11 trong s\u1ed1 21 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, Kovacic c\u00f3 109 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ea3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3. H\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Kovacic c\u0169ng ra s\u00e2n 5 trong 7 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Croatia nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 24, Kovacic c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. Pirlo c\u0169ng t\u1eebng m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y quanh anh. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real Madrid l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho Kovacic. Chelsea ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 cho Kovacic khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic\" title=\"Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/161353-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 sau khi c\u00f3 Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft l\u00e0 Jorginho. C\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 con thoi c\u1ee7a Kante. Chelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 trong tay nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Kovacic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00fap Kovacic c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Kovacic c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 HLV Sarri b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u00f3, Kovacic m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay v\u00ec b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201ck\u00e9p ph\u1ee5\u201d h\u1ea1ng sang nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-niu-keo-hazard-o-lai-sau-khi-mat-courtois-172-194106.html\">Sao Chelsea n\u00edu k\u00e9o Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau khi m\u1ea5t Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-ma-kepa-arrizabalaga-tan-binh-71-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea-172-194099.html\">Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 Kepa Arrizabalaga \u2013 T\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2172","checkdouble":"194118"},{"date":"16:52 09/08","title":"2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/2-doi-bong-o-ligue-1-dai-chien-vi-rakitic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n mua Rakitic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p duy nh\u1ea5t Verratti l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/2-doi-bong-o-ligue-1-dai-chien-vi-rakitic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Rakitic, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i PSG v\u00e0 Monaco th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-bang-sao-khung-cua-barca-172-182166.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Rakitic</span>, Mourinho nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco c\u00f3 Rakitic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Ivan Rakitic b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i sau khi \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Iniesta.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" title=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/liverpool-tranh-ivan-rakitic-voi-mu-trong-mua-he-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ivan Rakitic r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1edfi Monaco kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi PSG n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Rakitic r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd vi ph\u1ea1m Lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf Ligue 1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Rakitic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Barca. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Monaco v\u00e0 PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Rakitic l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2171","checkdouble":"194119"},{"date":"17:07 09/08","title":"Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mourinho-bi-quan-ve-kha-nang-mua-them-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vui v\u1ebb cho l\u1eafm.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Premier League ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 v\u1edbi 3 t\u00e2n binh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c khi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin l\u1eafm. TTCN s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay, v\u00ec v\u1eady gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 n\u00f3. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00ecnh \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" title=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mourinho-bi-quan-ve-kha-nang-mua-them-nguoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u00f3i v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. S\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u trong to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 8 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 3 Premier League, nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-scholes-du-doan-mu-nup-bong-man-city-mourinho-ra-duong-172-194105.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/paul-scholes-du-doan-mu-nup-bong-man-city-mourinho-ra-duong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-scholes-du-doan-mu-nup-bong-man-city-mourinho-ra-duong-172-194105.html\">Paul Scholes d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: MU n\u00fap b\u00f3ng Man City, Mourinho ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu-172-194089.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/9/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu-172-194089.html\">Wayne Rooney: MU ch\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nWayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2170","checkdouble":"194120"},{"date":"17:13 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \"bom x\u1ecbt\" c\u1ee7a Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham quan t\u00e2m Lucas Perez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ban-hop-dong-thu-9-cua-west-ham-den-tu-arsenal-172-193962.html\" target=\"_blank\">West Ham quan t\u00e2m Lucas Perez</span> c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham mua Lucas Perez t\u1eeb Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham mua Lucas Perez t\u1eeb Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/CHINH-THUC-West-Ham-mua-Lucas-Perez-tu-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>West Ham quan t\u00e2m Lucas Perez\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Deportivo de La Coruna theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, song kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay Lacazette, Aubameyang v\u00e0 Welbeck, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i West Ham th\u00ec Sporting Lisbon c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5\u00a0n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>West Ham ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a West Ham \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, sau Ryan Fredericks, Lukasz Fabianski, Issa Diop, Jack Wilshere, Aindriy Yarmolenko, Fabian Balbuena v\u00e0 Felipe Anderson.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>West Ham mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng song theo Sky Sport \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Perez West Ham \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 8 tri\u1ec7u euro. Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi West Ham ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn West Ham, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi West Ham\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cWest Ham c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Mario Husillos ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Perez \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Lucas \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a West Ham \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2169","checkdouble":"194121"},{"date":"17:08 09/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ch\u1ecdn B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/day-co-phai-ly-do-khien-hlv-park-hang-seo-loai-van-lam-chon-bui-tien-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 do ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 InStat th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh\u2019 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m do Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ch\u1ecdn B\u00f9i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ch\u1ecdn B\u00f9i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Dang-Van-Lam-bi-loai-khoi-Asiad-2018-Bat-ngo-nhung-hop-ly-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m h\u1eb3n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 InStat (ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin, s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7), ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00fd do ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo\u00a0ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m InStat c\u1eadp nh\u1eadp ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 193, c\u00f2n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c 187. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa so v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 243 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Oman, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 179 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 InStat c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u1eeba qua ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin cho Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf AFF Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay hay xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\">B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2168","checkdouble":"194122"},{"date":"17:39 09/08","title":"MU v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA 2018/19</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Bayern Munich, M.U \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester, Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester, Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Truoc-tran-gap-Leicester,-Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matic v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNemanja Matic, Sergio Romero, Marcos Rojo, Antonio Valencia, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Ander Herrera s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester. Matic, Romero v\u00e0 Dalot ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Rojo g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf World Cup 2018, Herrera v\u00e0 Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu H\u00e8 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cThi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng trong tay t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi ra 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Fred, Datlot v\u00e0 Lee Grant, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea b\u1ecf ra bi quan v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c BL\u0110 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nghich ly cua Jose Mourinho la luon tu tao ra dinh kien nhung lai nua muon thua nhan, nua khong.\" title=\"Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i n\u1eeda mu\u1ed1n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, n\u1eeda kh\u00f4ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/mourinho-xac-nhan-mu-vang-6-cau-thu-o-tran-gap-leicester-vi-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u00ean BL\u0110. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. BL\u0110 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu-172-194089.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rooney n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU</span>, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2167","checkdouble":"194123"},{"date":"10:10 09/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Top 4 Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/huyen-thoai-du-doan-bat-ngo-ve-top-4-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1eebng danh c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 2018/19 \u2013 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nShearer d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n 4 CLB d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Alan Shearer m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool d\u00f9 chi ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh tay, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n. 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Shearer cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1. Jurgen Klopp hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ti\u00eau, c\u00f2n h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ee9ng y\u00ean so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alan Shearer nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alan Shearer nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Alan-Shearer-nhan-dinh-Top-4-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alan Shearer&nbsp;nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 2018/19: Liverpool th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. Ai bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf? V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ngai v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Man City m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng CLB n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i Top 4, theo t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Man City v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00ec h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; &ndash; Alan Shearer nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Top 4 Premier League 2018/19.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;&#10; mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:&#10; 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\">\r\n            <td width=\"100%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:100.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a   Shearer v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1. Man City</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2. Liverpool</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3. Man United</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4. Tottenham</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">5. Chelsea</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">6. Arsenal</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shearer-dung-voi-gach-ten-mu-khoi-danh-sach-ung-vien-vo-dich-172-194084.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/shearer-dung-voi-gach-ten-mu-khoi-danh-sach-ung-vien-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shearer-dung-voi-gach-ten-mu-khoi-danh-sach-ung-vien-vo-dich-172-194084.html\">Shearer: S\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean M.U kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean BBC, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Alan Shearer cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1ea1t t\u00ean M.U kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua-172-194039.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua-172-194039.html\">Pep Guardiola: Man City s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u01a1n n\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2166","checkdouble":"194088"},{"date":"10:55 09/08","title":"Wayne Rooney: \"MU ch\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 n\u1ebfu...\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/9/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rooney mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, M.U m\u1edbi chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d. HLV Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney muon la dien vien chinh\" title=\"Rooney mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean ch\u00ednh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2013/10/rooneyichky3-20131010212615.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00f4ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng 50% y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 55 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng M.U s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Khi m\u00e0 Man City r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh c\u00f2n Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, n\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng BL\u0110 s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 cho Mourinho th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh. Mourinho \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o. H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Wayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Wayne-Rooney-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-cho-mu-them-mot-co-hoi-chieu-mo-alderweireld-172-194081.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU quan t\u00e2m Toby Alderweireld </span>c\u1ee7a Tottenham, ngo\u00e0i ra nh\u1eefng Harry Maguire (Leicester), Boateng (Bayern Munich) v\u00e0 Zouma (Chelsea) c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea hay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2165","checkdouble":"194089"},{"date":"11:33 09/08","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mu-chot-tuong-lai-paul-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao. Ch\u1ec9 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u1edbi 54 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn The Blues ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 mang anh v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh London.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kepa t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Courtois</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Kepa thi \u0111\u1ea5u 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb song b\u1eaft r\u1ea5t hay</em>&rdquo;, HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Chelsea t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 Kepa, Sarri th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Blues r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n g\u00ec su\u1ed1t v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chelsea-chieu-mo-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-thanh-cong-tu-Athletic-Bilbao-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ecfa gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1edbi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Trong khi Courtois mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec Chelsea ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e0 n\u1eeda ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3. Ngay sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u1ecd d\u00e0nh cho tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb v\u1edbi Courtois. \u0110\u00e3 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p, anh v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, Courtois m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c l\u00e1nh m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf. Sau khi c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, The Blues ch\u1ed1t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n Kepa Arrizabalaga. Ph\u00eda Bilbao th\u00ec d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi h\u1ecd h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh b\u1ea1o k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) v\u1edbi Kepa. Sau khi gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 n\u00e0y, th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 n\u1ed9p l\u00ean tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a La Liga, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Kepa Chim s\u1ebb c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang t\u1ea1i London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Kepa Chim s\u1ebb c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang t\u1ea1i London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kepa-arrizabalaga-chim-se-co-hot-vang-tai-london.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp 24, Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua con s\u1ed1 63 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson t\u1eeb Roma c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 3 tu\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i \u1edf ch\u1ed7, Kepa \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft 54 tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Bilbao tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Kepa \u1edf Real Valladolid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 (cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Bilbao) l\u00e0 Miguel \u00c1ngel Portugal l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. &ldquo;<em>Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Kepa c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1eabu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Phong c\u00e1ch \u01b0a th\u00edch l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi HLV Sarri</em>&rdquo;, Portugal chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Kepa\" title=\"thu mon Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Kepa-Arrizabalaga-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-Courtois-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u00f9ng Bilbao v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00ean l\u1ecbch ra m\u1eaft, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino P\u00e9rez c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee7y th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi HLV c\u1ee7a Real khi \u0111\u00f3: Zinedine Zidane d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Los Blancos l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n bao g\u1ed3m Keylor Navas, Kiko Casilla v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Luca Zidane, con trai Zizou. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft trong vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Kepa, song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn nghe theo \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Kepa, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Bilbao k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, ch\u00e0ng trai 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa Arrizabalaga th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa va Courtois\" title=\"Kepa va Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kepa-va-Courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thay th\u1ebf Courtois t\u1ea1i Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Chim s\u1ebb&rdquo; c\u00f3 h\u00f3t vang?</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Kepa c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh El Jilguero (Chim s\u1ebb c\u00e1nh v\u00e0ng). Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng pha bay l\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0 chim, anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau th\u00edch lo\u00e0i v\u1eadt n\u00e0y. Ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea ch\u01a1i chim c\u1ee7a anh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y Kepa ra m\u1eaft Chelsea, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta l\u1ea1i v\u00ed anh nh\u01b0 ch\u00fa chim s\u1ebb \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u1eafng m\u01b0a th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng London. Su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, Chelsea r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i l\u00e2m v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa thich choi chim tu nho\" title=\"Kepa thich choi chim tu nho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kepa-thich-choi-chim-tu-nho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa th\u00edch ch\u01a1i chim t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Kepa \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea. HLV Sarri d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ng\u1eafn, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i The Blues. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i Man City, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i theo phong c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ecdn Kepa thay v\u00ec ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke City. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Kepa t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga bat chac tay truoc Real\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga bat chac tay truoc Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/19/Kepa-Arrizabalaga-bat-chac-tay-truoc-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00c1p l\u1ef1c d\u00e0nh cho ch\u00e0ng trai 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ng\u00e0n c\u00e2n \u0111\u00e8 l\u00ean vai, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho Kepa. \u0110\u1ebfn David De Gea trong 1, 2 m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u khi t\u1edbi Man United c\u0169ng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a M.U. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Chelsea c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng Kepa s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nhanh h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e0n anh. Th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Portugal \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o El Jilguero s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y: &ldquo;<em>Kepa c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch n\u00e0o</em>&rdquo;, \u00f4ng k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n<span>V\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Kepa c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f9ng chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/9/Kepa-Arrizabalaga.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-sieu-cup-anh-2018-thanh-bai-cua-sarri-va-bai-hoc-man-city-cho-chelsea-172-193820.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018: Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Sarri v\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc Man City cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-172-193809.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Napoli phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u1ed7i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2164","checkdouble":"194090"},{"date":"10:45 09/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Kepa c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n10 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn&rdquo; khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Kepa Arrizabalaga v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro (71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng). S\u1edf d\u0129 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1i cao \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 qua m\u1eb7t Atletic Bilbao, gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 23 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Alisson Becker c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ngao ng\u00e1n v\u00ec qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft (67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 Ederson). Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 2 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a The Blues, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00fat b\u1ecf g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: Kepa v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/kep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: Kepa v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1, khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (35 tri\u1ec7u euro). S\u1edf d\u0129 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t r\u1ebb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1edfi anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 6 qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u1edbi Italia, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Brazil s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed7i qu\u1ed1c gia 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Anh (